description: Revenue for utilities industries across the U.S. was $149.1 billion for the 1st quarter of 2019, a 1.6 percent decrease from the previous quarter.

storyTitle: Food industry's Q1 income down 42%
description: The food industry's after-tax income in the first quarter of 2019 was down 42 percent over the same period last year, according to the U.S. Census Bureau.

storyTitle: New home sales in the South down in December 2019 compared to last year
description: The estimated sales of new homes in the South for the month of December 2019 was 347,000, compared to 351,000 for the same month the previous year.

storyTitle: New home sales in the United States up in December 2019 compared to last year
description: The estimated sales of new homes in the United States for the month of December 2019 was 694,000, compared to 564,000 for the same month the previous year.

storyTitle: New home sales in the South up in November 2019 compared to last year
description: The estimated sales of new homes in the South for the month of November 2019 was 400,000, compared to 367,000 for the same month the previous year.

storyTitle: New home sales in the United States up in November 2019 compared to last year
description: The estimated sales of new homes in the United States for the month of November 2019 was 719,000, compared to 615,000 for the same month the previous year.
